maxProfit(int[], int) - Static method in class Problem1_RodCutting.BruteForceSolution
Main method for the Brute Force approach for the Rod Cutting Problem, here we are taking a recursive approach, keep moving the left end of the rod while trying to figure out the maximum profit possible to cut the rest of the rod while keeping the right portion of the rod fixed each iteration.
maxProfit(int[], int) - Static method in class Problem1_RodCutting.DynamicProgrammingSolution
Main method of the dynamic programming solution, the gist of this algorithm is to memorize the max profit from cutting a rod of length i so that this piece of information can later be used when needed.
